{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8",
    "translationId": "rsv",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 8,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 8 in Revised Standard Version."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.1",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:1",
      "text": "Benjamin was the father of Bela his first-born, Ashbel the second, Aharah the third,",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.2",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:2",
      "text": "Nohah the fourth, and Rapha the fifth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.3",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:3",
      "text": "And Bela had sons: Addar, Gera, Abihud,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.4",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:4",
      "text": "Abishua, Naaman, Ahoah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.5",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:5",
      "text": "Gera, Shephuphan, and Huram.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.6",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:6",
      "text": "These are the sons of Ehud (they were heads of fathers' houses of the inhabitants of Geba, and they were carried into exile to Manahath):",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.7",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:7",
      "text": "Naaman, Ahijah, and Gera, that is, Heglam, who was the father of Uzza and Ahihud.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.8",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:8",
      "text": "And Shaharaim had sons in the country of Moab after he had sent away Hushim and Baara his wives.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.9",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:9",
      "text": "He had sons by Hodesh his wife: Jobab, Zibi-a, Mesha, Malcam,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.10",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:10",
      "text": "Jeuz, Sachia, and Mirmah. These were his sons, heads of fathers' houses.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.11",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:11",
      "text": "He also had sons by Hushim: Abitub and Elpaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.12",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:12",
      "text": "The sons of Elpaal: Eber, Misham, and Shemed, who built Ono and Lod with its towns,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.13",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:13",
      "text": "and Beriah and Shema (they were heads of fathers' houses of the inhabitants of Aijalon, who put to flight the inhabitants of Gath);",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.14",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:14",
      "text": "and Ahio, Shashak, and Jeremoth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.15",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:15",
      "text": "Zebadiah, Arad, Eder,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.16",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:16",
      "text": "Michael, Ishpah, and Joha were sons of Beriah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.17",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:17",
      "text": "Zebadiah, Meshullam, Hizki, Heber,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.18",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:18",
      "text": "Ishmerai, Izliah, and Jobab were the sons of Elpaal.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.19",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:19",
      "text": "Jakim, Zichri, Zabdi,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.20",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:20",
      "text": "Eli-enai, Zillethai, Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.21",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:21",
      "text": "Adaiah, Beraiah, and Shimrath were the sons of Shime-i.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.22",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:22",
      "text": "Ishpan, Eber, Eliel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.23",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:23",
      "text": "Abdon, Zichri, Hanan,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.24",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:24",
      "text": "Hananiah, Elam, Anthothijah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.25",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:25",
      "text": "Iphdeiah, and Penuel were the sons of Shashak.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.26",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:26",
      "text": "Shamsherai, Shehariah, Athaliah,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.27",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:27",
      "text": "Ja-areshiah, Elijah, and Zichri were the sons of Jeroham.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.28",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:28",
      "text": "These were the heads of fathers' houses, according to their generations, chief men. These dwelt in Jerusalem.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.29",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:29",
      "text": "Je-iel the father of Gibeon dwelt in Gibeon, and the name of his wife was Maacah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.30",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:30",
      "text": "His first-born son: Abdon, then Zur, Kish, Baal, Nadab,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.31",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:31",
      "text": "Gedor, Ahio, Zecher,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.32",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:32",
      "text": "and Mikloth (he was the father of Shime-ah). Now these also dwelt opposite their kinsmen in Jerusalem, with their kinsmen.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.33",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:33",
      "text": "Ner was the father of Kish, Kish of Saul, Saul of Jonathan, Malchishua, Abinadab, and Eshbaal;",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.34",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:34",
      "text": "and the son of Jonathan was Merib-baal; and Merib-baal was the father of Micah.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.35",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:35",
      "text": "The sons of Micah: Pithon, Melech, Tarea, and Ahaz.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.36",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:36",
      "text": "Ahaz was the father of Jehoaddah; and Jehoaddah was the father of Alemeth, Azmaveth, and Zimri; Zimri was the father of Moza.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.37",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:37",
      "text": "Moza was the father of Bine-a; Raphah was his son, Ele-asah his son, Azel his son.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.38",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:38",
      "text": "Azel had six sons, and these are their names: Azrikam, Bocheru, Ishmael, She-ariah, Obadiah, and Hanan. All these were the sons of Azel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.39",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:39",
      "text": "The sons of Eshek his brother: Ulam his first-born, Jeush the second, and Eliphelet the third.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "rsv:first-chronicles.8.40",
      "translationId": "rsv",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 8:40",
      "text": "The sons of Ulam were men who were mighty warriors, bowmen, having many sons and grandsons, one hundred and fifty. All these were Benjaminites.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
